<p>-To be fair to all bidders, I do not end auctions early or give out my reserve price.</p>
<p>-I need a response from the winning bidder within 3 days of the auction end, and payment must be received within&nbsp;5 days of the auction end.&nbsp; I only accept Paypal as payment for this item.</p>
<p>-Domestic insured shipping is included with this item.&nbsp; Internationally I&nbsp;can ship this item by Global Express Mail, or by International Registered Mail (as these are the only two that allow for tracking).&nbsp; International auction winners must email me at the end of the auction to get the shipping amount and total.&nbsp; However, prices are available at USPS.com to help you estimate before you bid.</p>
<p>-I reserve the right to cancel bids that I feel are not serious, and I can no longer accept bids from bidders with zero or only negative feedback.&nbsp; </p>
<p>-The items that I sell are as described to the best of my abilities, and I will accurately describe both the physical and mechanical (running)&nbsp;condition in the listing.&nbsp;&nbsp;Most of the watches that&nbsp;we list for auction have been cleaned and serviced, but others have not.&nbsp; I will&nbsp;always&nbsp;address this in the item description.&nbsp; If I have not had the watch serviced myself, then it is possible that servicing may be necessary, as with all vintage watches.&nbsp; </p>
<p>-If you have any questions about the item, my policies, or my feedback, please email me any questions before bidding&nbsp;and I will get back to you as soon as possible.&nbsp; Please do not assume things that are not in the listing, email me, I will be happy to answer your questions.&nbsp; </p>
<p>-All of the items that I sell are <strong>Genuine</strong>.</p>
<p>-Please take a look at my other items, and add me to your favorites!&nbsp;<strong><u><font color="#002cfd" size="5"> Be sure to check out&nbsp;our store.</font></u></strong>&nbsp; I will be listing new items often, including: watches, watch parts, and antique/vintage items as well.</p>
<p>-I always leave feedback for&nbsp;my auctions after it has been left for me.&nbsp; Thanks for looking, and I appreciate your bids!</p>')
