<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center" align="center"><span><strong><font color="#00008b">These are fine&nbsp;individually handcrafted models of the world’s most famous&nbsp;and revered aircraft and ships, faithfully reproduced in kiln-dried Mahogany wood.<o:p></o:p></font></strong></span></p>
